In his youth, Aldric was an adventurer of some renown, traveling with the Company of the Silver Dawn. He retired after the disastrous expedition to Blackstone Keep, where he lost his sword arm and all but two of his companions. The experience left him cautious—some say overly so.

Despite his conservative nature, Aldric recognizes that sometimes heroes must rise. He keeps a chest of his old adventuring gear in his home, and those who earn his trust may find him a valuable source of knowledge about the realm's dangers and secrets.`,
 
